- Here you go.
- Thank you.

62
00:04:44,799 --> 00:04:48,132
So you called last night, right?

63
00:04:49,599 --> 00:04:54,555
After I called him, we met up.

64
00:04:54,555 --> 00:04:58,732
Oh, you met up. That's progress.

65
00:04:59,699 --> 00:05:02,165
Speaking of which,

66
00:05:03,332 --> 00:05:08,598
