Actually… I don't remember anything.

70
00:05:23,298 --> 00:05:25,165
What?

71
00:05:26,032 --> 00:05:31,883
Did something happen last night?

72
00:05:38,165 --> 00:05:39,898
You totally messed up!

73
00:05:39,898 --> 00:05:43,265
Hey! Don't laugh!

74
00:05:43,265 --> 00:05:46,839
That was my first time drinking so much in my life.

75
00:05:46,839 --> 00:05:48,498
Sorry, sorry.

76
00:05:48,498 --> 00:05:51,999
So you don't know if you're dating?

77
00:05:52,598 --> 00:05:55,732
