79
00:05:57,965 --> 00:06:02,932
That's the point. He didn't react.

80
00:06:04,565 --> 00:06:06,265
So you were dumped.

81
00:06:06,265 --> 00:06:08,432
No!

82
00:06:09,498 --> 00:06:13,598
Wait, I don't know.

83
00:06:13,598 --> 00:06:16,059
If he likes you, he would have reacted, right?

84
00:06:16,059 --> 00:06:19,465
I understand you don't want to think that way.

85
00:06:19,465 --> 00:06:21,223
Perhaps you should move on.

86
00:06:21,223 --> 00:06:22,811
No.

87
00:06:23,565 --> 00:06:26,365
I'd rather take this as an opportunity

88
00:06:26,365 --> 00:06:28,571
to make him notice me.

89
00:06:30,132 --> 00:06:33,799
I didn't expect you to be so tough.

90
00:06:36,465 --> 00:06:38,265
Because

91
00:06:39,165 --> 00:06:44,831
he is the reason I became who I am now.

92
00:06:44,831 --> 00:06:47,732
Just be confident and be yourself.

93
00:06:48,532 --> 00:06:54,375
I can't give up this feeling so easily.

94
00:06:56,798 --> 00:06:58,965
I'll eat now.

95
00:07:06,165 --> 00:07:07,998
Hey.

96
00:07:09,132 --> 00:07:11,598
You're quite cool.

97
00:07:12,465 --> 00:07:14,167
Excuse me?

98
00:07:14,167 --> 00:07:15,965
Nothing.

99
00:07:16,598 --> 00:07:20,832
I am here to show you my perfect strategy.

100
00:07:20,832 --> 00:07:22,798
Let's go there together again.

101
00:07:22,798 --> 00:07:24,232
What shall we eat next time?

102
00:07:24,232 --> 00:07:25,665
Really?

103
00:07:25,665 --> 00:07:27,132
I agree.

104
00:07:27,132 --> 00:07:29,023
Usuda-san.

105
00:07:29,023 --> 00:07:30,807
Coming.

106
00:07:43,832 --> 00:07:46,132
I'm so nervous.

107
00:07:46,132 --> 00:07:48,665
Straightforwardly ask him out.

108
00:07:48,665 --> 00:07:50,270
Find if he's interested in you.

109
00:07:50,270 --> 00:07:51,380
[Mission: Make a date; assess it.]

110
00:07:51,380 --> 00:07:54,165
I want to go on a date with him.
[Shioya]

111
00:07:54,165 --> 00:07:56,255
If he has feelings for you,

112
00:07:56,255 --> 00:07:58,551
he should agree to go on a date.
[Shioya]

113
00:07:58,551 --> 00:08:00,365
Send a message not too formal or casual,
[Thanks for helping me.]

114
00:08:00,365 --> 00:08:03,795
that is hard to refuse.
[If it's not much trouble]

115
00:08:03,795 --> 00:08:05,215
It's so hard.

116
00:08:05,215 --> 00:08:06,310
Don't be afraid.
[Shall we go out this weekend?]

117
00:08:06,310 --> 00:08:08,660
The key is courage.

118
00:08:08,663 --> 00:08:10,265
"Courage."

119
00:08:10,965 --> 00:08:12,698
Courage!

120
00:08:16,732 --> 00:08:18,665
Send.

121
00:08:19,819 --> 00:08:21,767
Well done.
[Mission Complete!]

122
00:08:32,132 --> 00:08:34,232
[Sure. Is Sunday okay?]

123
00:08:34,232 --> 00:08:36,798
He replied instantly.

124
00:08:38,898 --> 00:08:41,132
It's so good to be alive!

125
00:08:41,132 --> 00:08:45,598
This means he likes me, right?

126
00:08:47,932 --> 00:08:49,732
Wait.

127
00:08:51,165 --> 00:08:53,932
I shouldn't be over excited,

128
00:08:54,632 --> 00:08:59,432
before his response to my confession is confirmed.

129
00:09:01,798 --> 00:09:05,665
I had planned to be calm.

130
00:09:09,465 --> 00:09:11,298
Sato-san?

131
00:09:11,865 --> 00:09:15,465
But Shioya-san is so handsome today, as always.

132
00:09:15,465 --> 00:09:18,795
The whole world is shining.

133
00:09:18,795 --> 00:09:23,265
Thank you, God.

134
00:09:23,932 --> 00:09:26,465
Is something wrong?

135
00:09:28,032 --> 00:09:31,932
Please don't worry. Let's go.

136
00:09:49,232 --> 00:09:53,198
You're not watching penguins but people.

137
00:09:53,832 --> 00:09:56,083
I plan to conduct a preliminary survey.

138
00:09:56,083 --> 00:09:57,765
"A survey"?

139
00:09:57,765 --> 00:10:02,232
There's a marine life exhibition proposal.

140
00:10:03,498 --> 00:10:05,503
Oh, the project Mizoguchi got?

141
00:10:05,503 --> 00:10:07,191
Yes.

142
00:10:07,832 --> 00:10:10,498
I plan to take some notes.

143
00:10:10,498 --> 00:10:13,798
Seals are also very popular.

144
00:10:13,798 --> 00:10:16,732
Also, peculiar creatures

145
00:10:16,732 --> 00:10:19,965
like spotted garden eel and umbrella octopus.

146
00:10:20,698 --> 00:10:24,132
The undersea world is profound and fascinating.

147
00:10:24,132 --> 00:10:27,363
I want to work hard to create a proposal

148
00:10:27,363 --> 00:10:29,899
that more people can see.

149
00:10:31,465 --> 00:10:34,431
You're still as enthusiastic as ever.

150
00:10:36,965 --> 00:10:38,765
Oh no.

151
00:10:39,365 --> 00:10:41,132
Well, Shioya-san.

152
00:10:43,199 --> 00:10:47,132
