233
00:19:20,432 --> 00:19:22,365
We can ignore it.

234
00:19:23,399 --> 00:19:25,711
But…

235
00:19:29,130 --> 00:19:31,911
It could be urgent.

236
00:19:48,030 --> 00:19:49,332
We can ignore it.
[Mizoguchi]

237
00:19:49,332 --> 00:19:52,065
But that's Mizoguchi-san!

238
00:19:55,430 --> 00:19:57,132
Hello.

239
00:20:06,690 --> 00:20:08,410
Oh.

240
00:20:10,390 --> 00:20:12,739
That's no longer important.

241
00:20:20,499 --> 00:20:22,299
Got it.

242
00:20:24,365 --> 00:20:26,659
I'll contact you tomorrow.

243
00:20:30,365 --> 00:20:34,595
Now? I'm with Sato-san.

244
00:20:35,590 --> 00:20:37,471
You want to talk to her?

245
00:20:38,460 --> 00:20:41,287
But if you say that…

246
00:20:44,065 --> 00:20:45,765
Here you go.

247
00:20:48,390 --> 00:20:52,032
It's… powered off.

248
00:20:52,790 --> 00:20:54,765
When did it shut off?

249
00:20:54,765 --> 00:20:56,665
At the call's start.

250
00:20:59,700 --> 00:21:03,065
Shioya-san.

251
00:21:05,190 --> 00:21:06,998
You're naughty.

252
00:21:08,098 --> 00:21:09,915
I suppose.

253
00:21:13,060 --> 00:21:17,415
You are so cute when you try to be quiet.

254
00:21:22,335 --> 00:21:26,691
♫ Indulge until I can barely stand ♫

255
00:21:26,691 --> 00:21:31,619
♫ Before getting dizzy, wave a goodbye ♫

256
00:21:31,619 --> 00:21:35,427
♫ Pour love and hate to fill the lack of innocence syndrome ♫

257
00:21:35,427 --> 00:21:37,851
♫ Give me more, give me more, give me more! ♫

258
00:21:37,851 --> 00:21:43,065
♫ Different, broken, melting instinct ♫

259
00:21:43,065 --> 00:21:48,332
I won't let anyone else hear you like this.

260
00:21:48,332 --> 00:21:50,565
It's for me only.

261
00:21:51,390 --> 00:21:53,632
Shioya-san.

262
00:21:56,890 --> 00:22:00,163
♫ Wobbling ♫

263
00:22:02,930 --> 00:22:04,183
Shioya.

264
00:22:04,183 --> 00:22:06,932
You shut off your phone purposely, right?

265
00:22:06,932 --> 00:22:08,711
You're overthinking it.

266
00:22:08,711 --> 00:22:12,671
Seriously, I wanted to report to you on what you said.

267
00:22:12,671 --> 00:22:14,254
What I mentioned?

268
00:22:14,254 --> 00:22:16,465
About Sato.

269
00:22:16,465 --> 00:22:20,027
I realized she's a good person.

270
00:22:20,027 --> 00:22:22,887
Why would such weird rumors spread?

271
00:22:26,495 --> 00:22:30,255
But I still hope she can improve her slow speed at work.

272
00:22:31,263 --> 00:22:33,365
Speaking of which,

273
00:22:33,365 --> 00:22:35,555
she mentioned that the handover didn't go smoothly.

274
00:22:35,555 --> 00:22:36,639
That's impossible.

275
00:22:36,639 --> 00:22:40,465
That was from Usuda-san who always focuses on work.

276
00:22:40,465 --> 00:22:43,398
She also gave her a very thick manual.

277
00:22:43,398 --> 00:22:45,375
"Manual"…

278
00:22:59,365 --> 00:23:04,132
I... will protect you.

279
00:23:07,460 --> 00:23:09,332
Kaede, you are my girlfriend, right?
